===========================================================================
|ID|OPERATOR                                   |NAME|EST.ROWS|EST.TIME(us)|
---------------------------------------------------------------------------
|0 |EXCHANGE IN REMOTE                         |    |11      |35          |
|1 |└─EXCHANGE OUT REMOTE                      |    |11      |26          |
|2 |  └─SORT                                   |    |11      |6           |
|3 |    └─NESTED-LOOP OUTER JOIN               |    |11      |4           |
|4 |      ├─TABLE FULL SCAN                    |A1  |1       |3           |
|5 |      └─MATERIAL                           |    |36      |8           |
|6 |        └─NESTED-LOOP OUTER JOIN CARTESIAN |    |36      |4           |
|7 |          ├─TABLE FULL SCAN                |A2  |6       |3           |
|8 |          └─MATERIAL                       |    |6       |3           |
|9 |            └─TABLE FULL SCAN              |A3  |6       |3           |
===========================================================================
