|5 |      └─HASH FULL OUTER JOIN         |     |11      |16          |
|6 |        ├─TABLE FULL SCAN            |A4   |9       |3           |
|7 |        └─SUBPLAN SCAN               |VIEW1|11      |10          |
|8 |          └─UNION ALL                |     |11      |10          |
