|10|            │ ├─HASH FULL OUTER JOIN |     |6       |7           |
|11|            │ │ ├─TABLE FULL SCAN    |A3   |6       |3           |
|12|            │ │ └─TABLE FULL SCAN    |A2   |6       |3           |
